    {
      "sort": 100000,
      "name": "Create a Scene",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "IeRRwtptKGvZCG1f",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>First things, first - create a Scene. You need to this for the GM Tools scene tool to be visible on the top left of the screen (the spanner and screwdriver icon). The current tools are:</p><ul><li><p>Winter Phase</p></li><li><p>Development Phase</p></li></ul><p></p><p>Restarting the game (including F5) will turn off the phases. If Winter Phase was active and you restart the game it will be turned off but the Game Year will not be advanced. You can always correct the year manually in the game settings.</p>"
      },
      "video": {
