    {
      "sort": 200000,
      "name": "Winter Phase",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "dXya6WfqQm63rD9C",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>Clicking on this will toggle the Winter Phase off or on (you will get a message at the top of the screen saying what the status is).</p><p></p><p>Opening the Winter Phase does several things:</p><ul><li><p>It creates a new History event for each character adding their passive Glory Total. The event is called \"Winter Phase\" and has the current Game Year shown (i.e. before the increase)</p></li><li><p>Activates the <strong>Winter Tab</strong> for all characters allowing them to carry out development (See @UUID[Compendium.Pendragon.instructions.JournalEntry.NKQVeB00DO4RfHEj.JournalEntryPage.JClE8n4rcuXssKLs]{Winter Phase} for more details).</p></li></ul><p>Closing the Winter Phase</p><ul><li><p>The Game Year is increased by 1 (which in turn adds 1 to the characters' ages)</p></li><li><p>Winter Phase is turned off for all actors and so they lose access to the <strong>Winter Tab</strong> on their character sheets</p></li></ul>"
      },
      "video": {
        "controls": true,
        "volume": 0.5
      },
      "src": null,
