    {
      "sort": 300000,
      "name": "Development Phase",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "H1y6R0ISSwpuKuMt",
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>This toggles the <strong>Winter Tab</strong> on and off for characters but without changing their age, the Game Year or adding a history event.</p><p></p><p>It will however reset the training status and will allow characters to improve skills, characteristics, passions and traits.</p><p></p><p>See @UUID[Compendium.Pendragon.instructions.JournalEntry.NKQVeB00DO4RfHEj]{Winter Phase} for more details of how to advance your character.</p>"
      },
