    {
      "sort": 500000,
      "name": "GM Roll",
      "type": "text",
      "_id": "33Wr4vXpMPVT85tz",
      "system": {},
      "title": {
        "show": true,
        "level": 1
      },
      "image": {},
      "text": {
        "format": 1,
        "content": "<p>This tool allows the GM to make a roll without having an actor.  You'll be asked to:</p><ul><li><p>Select the Roll Type</p></li><li><p>Enter a participant name (which appears on the chat card)</p></li><li><p>Enter the score you are rolling against</p></li></ul><p></p><p>The system will then follow the normal roll procedures.</p><p></p><p>There is also a macro included so the GM can add this to their hotbar.</p>"
      },
